  m_text: 'Queen: States if they are next to at least one ghost. Could be one ghost
    and one subject, or two subjects


    Jester: Either the Jester or another subject
    is the ghost. If the chosen subject isn''t the ghost, then the Jester is lying


    Maid:
    States a character is a ghost. Will always select subjects if lying, or ghosts
    if telling the truth


    Bard: States how far away they are from the closest
    ghost. If lying, states how far away they are from the closest subject'
